                    exit successfully\n  -y, --force                  Skip confirmations for destructive commands\n      --no-input               Never prompt; fail instead (useful for CI)\n  -v, --verbose                Enable verbose logging\n      --version                Print version and exit\n\nCommands:\n  send [flags]\n    Send an email (alias for 'gmail send')\n\n  ls (list) [flags]\n    List Drive files (alias for 'drive ls')\n\n  search (find) <query> ... [flags]\n    Search Drive files (alias for 'drive search')\n\n  open (browse) <target> [flags]\n    Print a best-effort web URL for a Google URL/ID (offline)\n\n  download (dl) <fileId> [flags]\n    Download a Drive file (alias for 'drive download')\n\n  upload (up,put) <localPath> [flags]\n    Upload a file to Drive (alias for 'drive upload')\n\n  login <email> [flags]\n    Authorize and store a refresh token (alias for 'auth add')\n\n  logout <email> [flags]\n    Remove a stored refresh token (alias for 'auth remove')\n\n  status (st) [flags]\n    Show auth/config status (alias for 'auth status')\n\n  me [flags]\n    Show your profile (alias for 'people me')\n\n  whoami (who-am-i) [flags]\n    Show your profile (alias for 'people me')\n\n  auth <command> [flags]\n    Auth and credentials\n\n  groups (group) <command> [flags]\n    Google Groups\n\n  admin <command> [flags]\n    Google Workspace Admin (Directory API) - requires domain-wide delegation\n\n  drive (drv) <command> [flags]\n    Google Drive\n\n  docs (doc) <command> [flags]\n    Google Docs (export via Drive)\n\n  slides (slide) <command> [flags]\n    Google Slides\n\n  calendar (cal) <command> [flags]\n    Google Calendar\n\n  classroom (class) <command> [flags]\n    Google Classroom\n\n  time <command> [flags]\n    Local time utilities\n\n  gmail (mail,email) <command> [flags]\n    Gmail\n\n  chat <command> [flags]\n    Google Chat\n\n  contacts (contact) <command> [flags]\n    Google Contacts\n\n  tasks (task) <command> [flags]\n    Google